description:
Description
Data on computer processors released between 2010 and 2020.
title: CPU's Released between 2010 and 2020.

parameters.process: Size of the process node used in production in nm.
parameters.boost_clock: Single-core max speed for the CPU in GHz.
parameters.socket: Specifies the type of connection to the motherboard.
parameters.name: Model name of the processor.
parameters.released: Date which the processor was released to the public.
parameters.tdp: Total draw power of the processor.
parameters.cores: Number of compute cores per processor.
parameters.base_clock: Base speed for the CPU in GHz.
parameters.l3_cache: Size of the level 3 cache on the processor in MB.
parameters.threads: The number of threads represents the number of simultaneous calculations that can be ongoing in the processor.
parameters.codename: Name given by manufacturer to all chips with this architecture.

format: A data frame with 875 rows and 12 variables.
